name: Frog Simulator (jkelly)
description:
Hoppety hop! Eat the flies, avoid the blackbird!

Frog Simulator was developed by Steven Benson and jkelly.

Minimum system requirements

Operating System: Windows 10 Version 18362.0 or higher

CPU: Intel Core i3-4170 or better

GPU: Nvidia GeForce GTX 1060 or better

HDD: 200 MB free space

RAM: 8 GB

VRAM: 6 GB
